### 7.5 Create user — weak password (expect 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/zrp/users/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username":         "weakuser",
  "first_name":       "Weak",
  "last_name":        "Pass",
